{"tid":796709,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《櫻桃小丸子》原作者櫻桃子離世　藝術家紛悼念","createTime":"2018-08-28T03:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T03:05:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6219246896b7ea3ae8fd389b152a9d78a23e638e","tid":796709,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"日本漫畫《櫻桃小丸子》原作者櫻桃子因乳癌在本月15日去世。這套經典漫畫紅遍亞洲地區，一直伴隨不少人成長。消息傳出後，不少漫畫家均透過各式各樣的創作，為櫻桃子送上最後的道別。<br />\n<br />\n香港設計師Kit Man及插圖師專頁「Mr &amp; Ms HK People」都透過小丸子的插圖創作，紀念離世的櫻桃子。而台灣方面的代表則包括插畫家Cherng及網上漫畫家微疼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/110106_e35d4bec4e6e6d06231c173c4a1a8f2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F110106_e35d4bec4e6e6d06231c173c4a1a8f2a.png&h=2d1aa598&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/110107_37a87b9fa9508f87b0d99d18cd5c3157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F110107_37a87b9fa9508f87b0d99d18cd5c3157.png&h=87b7306c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/110108_beea981751798534a58360dd1fa061c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F110108_beea981751798534a58360dd1fa061c9.png&h=b7cbe23a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/110143_484870b72c6ae154f7b3e1507a428df9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F110143_484870b72c6ae154f7b3e1507a428df9.png&h=1ff2132c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/櫻桃小丸子-原作者櫻桃子離世-藝術家紛悼念/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E6%AB%BB%E6%A1%83%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%B8%E5%AD%90-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E6%AB%BB%E6%A1%83%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96-%